Sentencas: Mn-Co alloys were electroplated on AISI 430 stainless steel using an electrodeposition technique with the aim to reduce oxidation and chromium volatilization.
Titulo: Fabrication of Mn-Co Alloys Electrodeposited on AISI 430 Ferritic Stainless Steel for SOFC Interconnect Applications

Sentencas: The electroplating parameters were designed to improve the coating quality.
Titulo: Fabrication of Mn-Co Alloys Electrodeposited on AISI 430 Ferritic Stainless Steel for SOFC Interconnect Applications

Sentencas: The increased current density with decreased MnSO4 content resulted in a denser coating layer.
Titulo: Fabrication of Mn-Co Alloys Electrodeposited on AISI 430 Ferritic Stainless Steel for SOFC Interconnect Applications

Sentencas: A sample coated with 0.10 M CoSO4 and 0.50 MnSO4 at 350 mA cm(-2) showed the best oxidation resistance after being oxidized at 800 degrees C for 90 h. The X-ray diffraction (XRD) result revealed that the oxide growth on the surface of the coated samples mainly formed oxides of MnCo2O4, MnCr2O4, and Cr2O3.
Titulo: Fabrication of Mn-Co Alloys Electrodeposited on AISI 430 Ferritic Stainless Steel for SOFC Interconnect Applications

Sentencas: The chromium volatilization was evaluated by exposing the coated samples to humidified synthetic air at 800 degrees C for 96 h. The mass flux of Cr volatilization was on the order of 10(-11)
Titulo: Fabrication of Mn-Co Alloys Electrodeposited on AISI 430 Ferritic Stainless Steel for SOFC Interconnect Applications

Sentencas: Furthermore, different heat treatments in O-2 and CO2 atmospheres were compared.
Titulo: Fabrication of Mn-Co Alloys Electrodeposited on AISI 430 Ferritic Stainless Steel for SOFC Interconnect Applications

Sentencas: Annealing in CO2 at 800 degrees C for 4 h helped increase the Mn-Co coating density.
Titulo: Fabrication of Mn-Co Alloys Electrodeposited on AISI 430 Ferritic Stainless Steel for SOFC Interconnect Applications

Sentencas: The relationship between the porosity and its failure behavior was also discussed.
